title: The 100-0 Holiday Mixer, ft. The Frisella Boys, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO200
itunes:title: The 100-0 Holiday Mixer, ft. The Frisella Boys, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO200
description: This 200th episode of our podcast is like the f*cking box of chocolates that your Aunt Paula is going to inhale this Christmas. It’s an educational and entertaining assortment of stories, rants, and practical insights about everything from being fearless and aggressive to raising 100-0 mindset kids and understanding that there’s really nothing you can’t bounce back from in life—except death. My dad and brother join me in the studio, so you know things get interesting real fast.
